<span class="com">| sum inStream |</span>
<span class="com">sum := 0.</span>
<span class="com">inStream := FileStream stdin bufferSize: 4096.</span>
<span class="com">[inStream atEnd] whileFalse: [</span>
<span class="com">   sum := sum + inStream nextLine asInteger].</span>
<span class="com"></span>
<span class="com">Transcript show: sum displayString; nl !</span>
